{"tid":107131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼壓床","createTime":"2017-02-04T08:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T18:07:04.000Z","uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82c5bfef6849e9df19af375c1e123585d29eb60b","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"幾年嚟每一個禮拜就有4-5次，以經知道點就會嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，求解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知叫睡眠癱瘓症好或鬼壓床好，求各位唔好屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a839b3549767245bfa48b8e5ff97934fa40cf44d","tid":107131,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:42:46.000Z","msg":"俾女鬼壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b134b51e5923fc533b6180d48fe728db8e460e8d","tid":107131,"uid":63160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"係咪多數出現係訓晏覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e5bb9e013b4378ca0a71f81a466601abdc9a2e","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾女鬼壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253922917c6518a43c565598d453ee3450670fb6","tid":107131,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"我想知點樣先會黎?<br />\n<br />\n樓主確認左係真鬼定純粹生理上既鬼壓床"},{"pid":"81fc7ee3fddb4ec6d36a5d2f2e7498e2b19b0c3c","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:44:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪多數出現係訓晏覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201d17582772da3f59a7db76c240d0b4f1071478","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:47:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想知點樣先會黎?<br />\n<br />\n樓主確認左係真鬼定純粹生理上既鬼壓床</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生理上，嚟料前（姐係瞓前） 抹大眼，影像會由全黑慢慢變做正常，眼鳴，週身唔自在。"},{"pid":"28671df2a976c6a80f1506c9f08df023f961f851","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想知點樣先會黎?<br />\n<br />\n樓主確認左係真鬼定純粹生理上既鬼壓床</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生理上，嚟料前（姐係瞓前） 抹大眼，影像會由全黑慢慢變做正常，眼鳴，週身唔自在。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知後如果唔洗面，繼續瞓5-10秒就嚟料，平均連續3-4次。"},{"pid":"02e8c31ab875cc4cba82049f2bf657b42de884ac","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8779224e2ce7c8293875baf09de36a4447bb3c","tid":107131,"uid":69483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:52:27.000Z","msg":"被壓完盡可能整醒自己，如果唔係再出現機會好高"},{"pid":"fdfa74d46ee9b9d1b03e21d63b06fb7aed1f9f6e","tid":107131,"uid":74315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:53:43.000Z","msg":"扎到慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85ca19b0b2e8db5621892ba1e915790151f36c4","tid":107131,"uid":53027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:54:23.000Z","msg":"講粗口啦"},{"pid":"32598c023718d5cfae99db5cabf16710492dd911","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被壓完盡可能整醒自己，如果唔係再出現機會好高</blockquote><br />\n係，連續3-4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2acc3cd786b07a5f66a07679ff7108ffc7fbf86","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扎到慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係，但咁落去好似開始有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f48883bb5057630f8f7cddfb79818e6c13264d","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:59:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講粗口啦</blockquote><br />\n講唔到嘢，手腳無法使用，呼吸困難。"},{"pid":"8092e0f4bbca08b5d0f3fcf7be4b863e748ea939","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"點先會斷到，雖然壓完之後發夢會有自覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d828ae22c81b5d2bd120161e4f7506d8a2166f","tid":107131,"uid":69483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>扎到慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係，但咁落去好似開始有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會開始變得怕訓覺，刻意搞到自己好攰先去訓，但反而容易被壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6054a20ed779f479ffd7eea4f7c7f9f9b19745bc","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>扎到慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係，但咁落去好似開始有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會開始變得怕訓覺，刻意搞到自己好攰先去訓，但反而容易被壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，越攰越易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204a998bf0b34268a32e6f8247044d24daaf0f1b","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f317dcfacac915b44a5d21c7c7b84736debe4f","tid":107131,"uid":38781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:19:40.000Z","msg":"近排好大壓力？訓前試下飲啲熱茶房擺香薰放鬆自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85ed12b69ffa3edb4cd2c43a7092d23018e9d69","tid":107131,"uid":75865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:23:04.000Z","msg":"我都成日咁，不過已經習慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5442bdd79f4832c2fbed620d0610f730e7f6670","tid":107131,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>被壓完盡可能整醒自己，如果唔係再出現機會好高</blockquote><br />\n係，連續3-4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時見人講點都同我有啲出入<br />\n但依位巴打同我情況好似<br />\n一定要令到個人醒 可能玩下電話或者落床去下廁所咁 如果唔係會無限Loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我琴晚先責完 仲要發夢中夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夢入面我比鬼責 之後就盡所能大癲大叫去醒 醒完過一陣就無事訓返 點知又突然醒左 先知頭先發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b91d3eb096cf092c7df169c9e24047cf4fafcc","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5957e20906988b4d57270dc63542279379b5e0a9","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:35:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近排好大壓力？訓前試下飲啲熱茶房擺香薰放鬆自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩三年了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cf440147c179166831bb22cbc1a7c92885664d","tid":107131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"大家係途中會點，我會自己知道，跟著等佢，好快就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}